                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> The rokurokubi is the target of an alchemical bomb Strike</p>\n<p><strong>Requirements</strong> The rokurokubi is aware of the attack, not flat-footed against it, and doesn't have a creature grabbed with their jaws</p>\n<hr />\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> The rokurokubi attempts to catch the flung bomb in their mouth. They gain a +4 circumstance bonus to AC against the triggering attack. If the attack misses, they catch the bomb in their mouth and harmlessly drink its contents down, regaining Hit Points equal to the bomb's item level.</p>"
